data.description: Welcome to this upgraded home in the heart of Dr. Phillips, Orlando, FL. As you approach the property, the meticulously paved driveway leads the way to both the garage and the inviting pool area, setting the tone for the modern upgrades throughout done in 2020.    This residence has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a convenient half bath at the pool, providing comfort and functionality for the entire family. The beautifully designed kitchen opens up to the spacious living room and dining area, creating an ideal setting for family gatherings. Featuring stainless steel appliances, a stylish backsplash, and top-quality granite countertops, this kitchen is a chef's dream.    The entire home is adorned with exquisite crown molding and illuminated by recessed lights, adding an extra touch of sophistication to every room.    The master bedroom has been transformed into a retreat, now featuring an expansive closet and a fully upgraded master bathroom. With new cabinets, countertops, and a luxurious spa with a walk-in shower, the master suite offers both comfort and elegance.    Step outside to discover a true Floridian oasis. The resurfaced pool, modern paving, and a generously sized backyard create a perfect space for outdoor activities. The extensive paved area allows for convenient storage of your recreational toys, be it boats, RVs, or 4x4 vehicles. Embrace the Florida sun as you relax in the pool and spa, complete with a pool heater for year-round enjoyment.    This home not only provides a haven of comfort but also situates you in the vibrant and central area of Dr. Phillips, Orlando. Indulge in the Florida lifestyle with easy access to renowned restaurants along Restaurant Row. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the best of Orlando living—schedule a visit to this exquisite home today!
